      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="title">
        Keyword Research for Improved Marketing Strategies.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        Keyword research is necessary before both web design and digital marketing. It can be redone many time as your business grows to understand where your best chance of lead generation is at the time. We track all our clients Google Search results through Search Console atleast twice a week when managing their SEO. Allowing for on the fly keyword optimisation that truly improves your rate of sales. With prior keyword planning for your brand from experts competing in high volume searches, your ad campaigns and organic lead generation will improve across the board. Expert digital marketing management on the Gold Coast.
      </Fragment>
