    <FirstProcess />

          <SectionHeadImg>
            <Fragment slot="smltitle">
              Compete in the keywords that matter most at that moment
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="title">
              On-the-fly keyword optimisation.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="desc">
              I believe that a well-crafted keyword strategy is the backbone of a successful online marketing campaign. It's not just about identifying relevant keywords; it's about aligning those keywords with your unique business goals and target audience. As an experienced digital marketer, I specialize in keyword strategy optimization, tailoring a plan that resonates with your audience, boosts your online visibility, and ultimately drives conversions. The online marketplace is highly competitive, and it's essential to stay ahead of the game. With competitive keyword research, I dive deep into your industry and discover the keywords your competitors may be overlooking. I'll identify untapped opportunities that allow you to gain an edge in search engine rankings and outperform others in your niche.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="cover">
              <img
                        src="/works/ax-sqr-cpc-results.webp"
                        class="w-full"
                      />
            </Fragment>
          </SectionHeadImg>

          <SectionHeadSecImg>
            <Fragment slot="smltitle">
              Keyword optimisation for competitive niches
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="title">
              Competitive Keyword Research.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="desc">
              Keyword research is more than just identifying popular phrases; it's about understanding the intent behind those keywords. I employ a methodical approach to keyword analysis, dissecting the searcher's intent and tailoring your content accordingly. By delving into the minds of your audience, I'll guide you in creating content that answers their questions, meets their needs, and drives them to engage with your business. I understand the importance of structuring your content strategically around your selected keywords. Through keyword mapping, I'll help you organize your website or content around specific target keywords. This not only optimizes your content for search engines but also ensures a cohesive user experience. I'm here to guide you through the process, from defining your primary and secondary keywords to incorporating them seamlessly into your content.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="cover">
              <img
                        src="/works/e-comm-results.webp"
                        class="w-full"
                      />
            </Fragment>
          </SectionHeadSecImg>

          <SectionHeadImg>
            <Fragment slot="smltitle">
              Helping give your brand the advantage
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="title">
              Finding low competition keywords.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="desc">
              In today's crowded online landscape, finding low competition keywords can provide your business with a significant advantage. These keywords often have less competition, making it easier to rank higher in search results. I'll share strategies for uncovering these hidden gems, ensuring your content gets the attention it deserves without facing stiff competition. Long-tail keywords can be a game-changer in your digital marketing strategy. I'll show you how to harness the power of these highly specific phrases to attract a more engaged and relevant audience. By optimizing for long-tail keywords, you can connect with potential customers who are further along in the decision-making process and are more likely to convert into leads or sales.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="cover">
              <img
                        src="/works/facebook-marketing-results.png"
                        class="w-full"
                      />
